The paper proposes a new model-free algorithm for trajectory optimization that uses backpropagation of a local quadratic time-dependent Q-Function to derive the policy update. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of policy updates and system dynamics, which are common topics in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions theoretical analysis, which is a common topic in Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
